{"tid":2515273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟委員會週一提議，將允許已接種疫苗的第三國遊客進入歐盟成員國","createTime":"2021-05-04T00:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T00:51:10.000Z","uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae120329deacf3e99903e6b381d3b966a14d7b6","tid":2515273,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:32:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.abc.es/sociedad/abci-bruselas-propone-permitir-entrada-union-europea-vacunados-terceros-paises-202105031219_noticia.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.es%2Fsociedad%2Fabci-bruselas-propone-permitir-entrada-union-europea-vacunados-terceros-paises-202105031219_noticia.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=1059dad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.abc.es/sociedad/abci-bruselas-propone-permitir-entrada-union-europea-vacunados-terceros-paises-202105031219_noticia.html</a><br />\n歐盟委員會週一提議，將允許已接種疫苗的第三國遊客進入歐盟成員國<br />\n<br />\n旅行者應在抵達前至少14天接種這種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟正準備推出一個歐洲健康證書，它希望在6月底前投入使用。到那時，成員國應該能夠接受歐盟以外國家頒發的證書，該文本說。<br />\n<br />\n然而，預計會有一個機制，在一個國家的疫情形勢惡化時，特別是由於突發的變異病毒而使歐盟能迅速暫停其入境。該提案現在必須提交給成員國，成員國將於週三審議該提案。"},{"pid":"7e479240bb77f2d04831637859b80142f100d86e","tid":2515273,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRrW4nZ1Yh3aHu42zAo9yfc2bMqkfQ9LqnydWR8HmEqQU?filename=6rWSokq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rWSokq.png&h=9600a327&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4035b4c5cb4052bd206a4de8c71463f52f1aacc","tid":2515273,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"包唔包4興先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4284f58a4377b3436d3cef65f1c9fabc72b47431","tid":2515273,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"唔包 fall